###

### ===== iPhone 15 Pro Variants =====

### Create Variant 1 - iPhone 15 Pro Black 128GB
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "sku": "IPHONE-15-PRO-BLK-128",
  "additionalPrice": 0,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "isActive": true,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/iphone15pro-black-128.jpg",
  "attributeValueIds": [
    "{{blackValueId}}",
    "{{storage128Id}}"
  ]
}

