### ===== QUERY OPERATIONS =====

### Get All Product Variants
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/variants/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Product Variants by Product ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/variants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Product Variant by ID
@variantId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Product Variant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "additionalPrice": 150,
  "stockQuantity": 100,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Product Variant
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/variants/{{variantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
